# {{math}} A ratio of one and a half to one. Found in mathematical texts, but rarely used by modern writers.  


===Usage notes===
Used by [[w:Sir Isaac Newton|Sir Isaac Newton]] in works such as his ''Principia'', ''Galileo'' and ''Dialogues''.

